# Mechigram — Platform

Applies to `cmd/`, `internal/`, CI. Role: `ia/roles/platform-engineer.md`.

- `cmd/mechigram/main.go` only parses flags and calls `app.Generate`
- Use `fmt.Errorf("...: %w", err)` — no `log.Fatal` outside main
- Wire `--board`, `--dict`, `--output`, `--seed`, `--format`, `--solution` per ROADMAP
- Retries with new seed belong in `internal/app`, not in solver

CI must run `go vet ./...`, `go test ./...`, `go build ./cmd/mechigram`.
